.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, raspberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rugby
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, tiparillo
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Food        | lime      | raspberry  |
| Sport       | rugby     | cricket    |
| Cigar   | chaman | tiparillo |

