.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-16::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice
2 different pets are kept: snake, mouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, water-polo
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice     |
| Pet        | mouse   | snake |
| Sport      | water-polo  | lacrosse  |

